name: Octo-Moji
body:
![](https://raw.github.com/sym3tri/octo-moji/master/extension/icons/icon-128.png)

### Installation
Install it from the Google Chrome Web Store

### Usage
Just type colon `:` to bring up the auto-complete menu.

### Authors and Contributors
Created by me (@sym3tri). More about me at [www.edrooth.com](http://www.edrooth.com)

### Support or Contact
Having trouble? Check out [the documentation](https://github.com/sym3tri/octo-moji/wiki) or [submit an issue](https://github.com/sym3tri/octo-moji/issues).
